reviewText: Loved this movie but definitely couldn't afford the Scream Factory release so I went for this instead. Very good quality for a film I like!

this is a awesome movie. For once the sequel is just as good as the first movie. this is a very good film though not as scary as the first but still good. the acting is great the story is great and the special effects are good. love this movie. dennis hopper is awesome in this movie and so is bob moseley and the guy who plays leatherface and jim siedow. great movie. if you have not seen this movie then i recommend you do
